<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>パスワード変更 - アルバイト管理システム</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>body { font-family: 'Hiragino Sans', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-indigo-50 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 w-full max-w-sm">
    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-indigo-700 mb-2">パスワードを設定してください</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">初回ログインのため、新しいパスワードを設定してください</p>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="bg-red-50 text-red-700 p-3 rounded-lg mb-4 text-sm"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/change-password">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">新しいパスワード</label>
        <input type="password" name="new_password" required minlength="8" autofocus
          class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500">
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">8文字以上で設定してください</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">パスワード（確認）</label>
        <input type="password" name="confirm_password" required
          class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-indigo-600 text-white py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 font-medium">設定して続ける</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
